attributes.Long form description: The student is to assemble the stool. First, the student aligns the two legs and screws them together with the bolt and hex nut. Next, the student attaches the legs to the seat. Lastly, the student screws in the screws at the four corners of the legs and seat.

attributes.Transcription: So, hello, thank you for agreeing for taking our study.
